events.text: I hope you enjoyed this little adventure.
I got a word from The Creator for you
They says you arrived in somewhat of a bad time, and the Dream Lands were missing some of it's contents.
You will need to wait for a little bit to see an improved version .  . .
The Creator says it was a really difficult project and even if it didn't look exactly like their dreams, it carries the esence of those places. . .
Now you should go, there is a lot of other Creators out there, with really interesting Dream Lands.
